---
description: Keep frontend implementation docs-first.
alwaysApply: true
---

`docs/` is the implementation source of truth for frontend work. Before changing
a route, page behavior, navigation, shared UX pattern, layout, design language,
data contract, architecture rule, or review rule, update the matching canonical
doc first.

If code and docs disagree, treat the PR as blocked until the same change either
updates the docs or brings the code back to the documented contract.
